Stefania La Greca is running for local elections in Campania in southern Italy . 
  Pictures of the Lega Sud Ausoni party candidate have gone viral . 
  The 36-year-old is hoping to represent Caldoro in the regional elections in May . 
  She has posted dozens of pictures of herself in skimpy bikinis . 
  But she has defended her pictures and denied using her looks to get votes . 
  She is standing for an independent party and wants her region to be independent . 
  She said she was born beautiful but complained about Italian attitudes to women . 
 